.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-COMPACT" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-compact \- run VACUUM on the wallet SQLite database
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-compact
.RI [ wallet ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Runs
.B VACUUM
on the wallet's SQLite database to reclaim free pages and reduce
file size.
Reports bytes saved.
Returns
.B {"ok":false}
if the database does not exist or the vacuum fails.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"ok":true,"before_bytes":N,"after_bytes":N,"saved_bytes":N}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-wallet-check (1),
.BR lightning-wallet-prune (1)
